{"tid":974482,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"華為透過空殼公司暗中在敘利亞經營業務","createTime":"2019-01-09T02:07:57.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-09T03:31:04.000Z","uid":54373,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"c37c7e1cfa6200cd358acc042c6779f17fe99d5b","tid":974482,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-09T02:07:57.000Z","msg":"《路透社》報道，華為集團與香港公司Skycom的關係比之前所知更加密切，華為還透過一間在毛里求斯註冊的空殼公司，發展在敘利亞的業務。<br />\n<br />\n《路透社》取得的文件指出，華為是透過這家在2006年成立的空殼公司，操控香港的Skycom。報道翻查香港的紀錄，指Skycom的股份在2007年11月售予這間空殼公司，並持股至少十年。<br />\n<br />\n文件又提到，華為一名高層在2011年12月出任Skycom在伊朗的業務經理兩年，而至少三名中國公民有華為及Skycom在伊朗銀行賬戶的簽名權。<br />\n<br />\n報道說，華為在敘利亞的公司看似解散，但他們仍透過不同公司繼續當地的經營，包括這間空殼公司，它直到2015年仍在當地設有辦公室。"},{"pid":"1f905d99ccc98372a98dd422b529546a2ea335a0","tid":974482,"uid":107364,"like":0,"dislike":10,"score":-10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-09T02:10:41.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"4d996933b2e71c6aafc1314e77f866d3807acd08","tid":974482,"uid":194415,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-09T02:12:01.000Z","msg":"8 號了<br />\n晚晚洲係咪冇引渡去美國？"},{"pid":"32d5f0b0fe210008015b4e495f8acd4ab87adc58","tid":974482,"uid":10890,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"4d996933b2e71c6aafc1314e77f866d3807acd08","tid":974482,"uid":194415,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-09T02:12:01.000Z","msg":"8 號了<br />\n晚晚洲係咪冇引渡去美國？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-09T03:31:04.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://globalnews.ca/news/4824007/trudeau-trump-phone-call-china-huawei/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fglobalnews.ca%2Fnews%2F4824007%2Ftrudeau-trump-phone-call-china-huawei%2F&d=Q7xW9EaYSPylzTvpwZPTJU%2Fk3Pi4b370HO%2BLvdN%2BZCE%3D&h=fa3ae5a1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://globalnews.ca/news/4824007/trudeau-trump-phone-call-china-huawei/</a><br />\n<br />\n侵侵同peoplekind傾電話講呢個topic<br />\n但冇人知兩個傾成點"}]}